{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-aprender-07-disjoint-set-union-find-markdown-remark-frontmatter-slug-tsx","path":"/aprender/07-disjoint-set-union-find/exercicios-1/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"05 - Exercícios","description":"Confira exercícios comentados","author":"Pedro Henrique Paiola, Rene Pegoraro, Wilson M Yonezawa"},"html":"<h2 id=\"c--beat-the-spread-uva--10812\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#c--beat-the-spread-uva--10812\" aria-label=\"c  beat the spread uva  10812 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>C – Beat the Spread! (UVA – 10812)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Problema</strong>: calcular, se possível, o placar de dois times a partir da soma <code>s</code> das pontuações e da diferença absoluta <code>d</code>.</li>\n<li>É garantido que os valores de entrada <code>s</code> e <code>d</code> são inteiros não negativos.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Considerando <code>x</code> como sendo a maior pontuação, e <code>y</code> a menor, podemos dizer que:\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 320px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/bb3f8e6e5917844d7e12a425d8a8e017/72799/img1.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 53.987730061349694%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='img1' title='' src='/static/bb3f8e6e5917844d7e12a425d8a8e017/72799/img1.png' srcset='/static/bb3f8e6e5917844d7e12a425d8a8e017/222b7/img1.png 163w,\n/static/bb3f8e6e5917844d7e12a425d8a8e017/72799/img1.png 320w' sizes='(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Resolvendo este sistema obtemos que:\n<span class='gatsby-resp-image-wrapper' style='position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; '>\n      <a class='gatsby-resp-image-link' href='/static/c69d89350f4ba9c7d19f9b7895c7d43a/cab8c/img2.png' style='display: block' target='_blank' rel='noopener'>\n    <span class='gatsby-resp-image-background-image' style=\"padding-bottom: 23.926380368098158%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class='gatsby-resp-image-image' alt='img2' title='' src='/static/c69d89350f4ba9c7d19f9b7895c7d43a/a6d36/img2.png' srcset='/static/c69d89350f4ba9c7d19f9b7895c7d43a/222b7/img2.png 163w,\n/static/c69d89350f4ba9c7d19f9b7895c7d43a/ff46a/img2.png 325w,\n/static/c69d89350f4ba9c7d19f9b7895c7d43a/a6d36/img2.png 650w,\n/static/c69d89350f4ba9c7d19f9b7895c7d43a/cab8c/img2.png 744w' sizes='(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px' style='width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;' loading='lazy' decoding='async'>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Analisando estas equações, e sabendo que a pontuação de cada time é sempre um inteiro positivo, podemos dizer que só é possível calcular <code>x</code> e <code>y</code> quando:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>𝑠 + 𝑑</code> e <code>𝑠 − 𝑑</code> são números pares.</li>\n<li><code>𝑠 − 𝑑 ≥ 0</code> ou, de forma equivalente, <code>𝑠 ≥ 𝑑</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"d--peters-smokes-uva--10346\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#d--peters-smokes-uva--10346\" aria-label=\"d  peters smokes uva  10346 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>D – Peter’s Smokes (UVA – 10346)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Problema</strong>: determinar quantos cigarros Peter pode possuir, sendo que ele começa com <code>n</code> cigarros e a cada <code>k</code> bitucas ele consegue enrolar um novo cigarro.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Este exercício pode ser resolvido apenas simulando o problema descrito:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-cpp line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">soma <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nbitucas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>bitucas <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> k<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    n <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> bitucas <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> k<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    soma <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    bitucas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> bitucas <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> k <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ncout <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> soma <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>"}},"pageContext":{"id":"a8451be3-bbc0-5a10-aeb5-1716c9f36b11","frontmatter__slug":"exercicios-1","__params":{"frontmatter__slug":"exercicios-1"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216"],"slicesMap":{}}